---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Inflection Point Partners">
	<!-- Page Intro -->
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
			<div class="mt-24 sm:mt-32 lg:mt-40">
				<div class="max-w-2xl">
					<h1>
						<span class="block font-display text-base font-semibold text-stone-800">About us</span>
						<span class="sr-only"> - </span>
						<span class="mt-6 block max-w-5xl font-display text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-stone-800 sm:text-6xl">
							Crafting spaces that inspire
						</span>
					</h1>
					<div class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl text-neutral-600">
						<p>
							Founded in 2018, Inflection Point Partners brings together a passionate team of designers, architects, and artisans dedicated to creating interiors that resonate with how people actually live.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<!-- Team Section -->
	<div class="mt-24 sm:mt-32 lg:mt-40">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none">
				<!-- Border -->
				<div class="border-t border-stone-300"></div>

				<!-- Arthur Campos -->
				<div id="arthur" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-800">
							Arthur Campos
						</h2>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Owner & Creative Director</p>
					</div>
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-neutral-600">
							<p>
								Arthur founded Inflection Point Partners with a vision to create spaces that transform the way people experience their homes and workplaces. With over two decades in the design industry, he has cultivated relationships with master craftspeople and suppliers across three continents.
							</p>
							<p>
								His philosophy centers on the belief that great design should feel inevitableâ€”as if the space could never have been any other way. Arthur oversees all client relationships and ensures every project reflects the studio's commitment to thoughtful, enduring design.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Border -->
				<div class="border-t border-stone-300 mt-24"></div>

				<!-- Claire Ashcraft -->
				<div id="claire" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-800">
							Claire Ashcraft
						</h2>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Principal Designer</p>
					</div>
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-neutral-600">
							<p>
								Claire joined Inflection Point Partners after fifteen years leading design at prestigious firms in London and New York. Her work has been featured in Architectural Digest, Elle Decor, and Wallpaper* magazine.
							</p>
							<p>
								With a background in fine arts from Central Saint Martins and interior architecture from the Royal College of Art, Claire brings a distinctive eye for proportion, texture, and light that defines the studio's signature aesthetic.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Border -->
				<div class="border-t border-stone-300 mt-24"></div>

				<!-- Marcus Whitener -->
				<div id="marcus" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-800">
							Marcus Whitener
						</h2>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Design Director</p>
					</div>
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-neutral-600">
							<p>
								Marcus oversees architectural integration and spatial planning across all projects. His decade of experience bridges the gap between architecture and interior design, ensuring every space flows naturally and functions beautifully.
							</p>
							<p>
								A graduate of UC Berkeley's architecture program, Marcus previously worked with renowned firms on hospitality and high-end residential projects throughout California and Asia.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Border -->
				<div class="border-t border-stone-300 mt-24"></div>

				<!-- Sofia Karter -->
				<div id="sofia" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:gap-8">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-800">
							Sofia Karter
						</h2>
						<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">Senior Designer</p>
					</div>
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
						<div class="space-y-6 text-base text-neutral-600">
							<p>
								Sofia brings Scandinavian minimalism and warmth to the studio's residential projects. Her talent for creating calm, light-filled spaces that feel both serene and inviting has earned her a devoted following among clients seeking thoughtful simplicity.
							</p>
							<p>
								Before joining Inflection Point Partners, Sofia spent eight years at a leading Stockholm design studio, where she developed her expertise in sustainable materials and biophilic design principles.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
